line_1: In vain proud Gaul with boastul Spain conspires,
line_2: When English valour English beauty fires;

line_1: Blest state! where ev'ry thing conspires
line_2: To fill the breast with heav'nly fires!

line_1: And ev'ry Grace to Speak the God conspires.
line_2: His Eye-balls lighten the Celestial Fires,
